N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 401.3 - Speed limit

State Regulations

No person shall operate a motor vehicle at a rate of
speed in excess of 30 miles per hour, or in excess of any lesser rate posted in
any zone or portion of a park road, parking area or any other travelable
way. Notes
